{"title":"我呼吁（外一首）——为义务植树的决议而写","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":3,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我呼吁（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为义务植树的决议而写"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田　间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在人大的会堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手高扬迎接春芳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上花香党给乳浆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的阳光照心脏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有金枝哪有富强？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有翠叶哪有风光？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"植树金锣铁鼓响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各路凤凰来飞翔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为子孙后代留荫凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿将生命作土壤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拟　格　言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀枝花这位新画师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金笔涂之于玉城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"樱花树她以那微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显示出青春与年少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们还贫穷，又富有千金”*"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的江山万古青青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的沃野重重新绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可为儿女作玉作书。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金的季节已到来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金之树应由我们栽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*引自胡乔木近作《诗六首》。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}